 Introduction
Todayâ€™s task in my DevOps 100 Days Challenge was about real-world troubleshooting.
Our production-like application suddenly couldnâ€™t connect to its database. After checking, we found the MariaDB service was down on the database server.

This task taught me how to:

read MariaDB logs,

understand socket/permission errors,

